  "keyFeatures": [
    "Turn-based card strategy gameplay with elemental mechanics (Air, Earth, Energy, Fire, Water)",
    "Colombian native animal characters (Bear, Condor, Chameleon, Frog) with multiple skins",
    "Team/faction system inspired by UNAL university faculties",
    "3D interactive dice rolling for turn mechanics",
    "Battle state machine with Start, Loop, Turn, Referee, and End phases",
    "AI bot opponents with random deck generation",
    "Collectible card system with value-based combat resolution",
    "Dialogue system integration via DialogueManager autoload",
    "Centralized scene, music, and flags management via Godot autoloads"
  ],
